commit.message: Probleme avec le transfert dobjet a travers les activites

Web Client

Half implementation of a web client. Fetching of plans works. Submitting information for quote works.

Prediction model is not functionnal for some reason. Will leave as is :)
Added quote activity and day of birth button

Revert "Merge remote-tracking branch 'origin/application' into javapp"

This reverts commit 3ad90014553eada7ce0f77f6e0d2b36fd21f1a4e.

Fixed persistence permission

Saves AI model in projet's folder instead of wherever Python feels like saving it (System32)

Implemented persistence of model & testing

Implemented save to disk of random forest model. Model accuracy is tested with 30% of the data.

Build model from 100.000 entries

Fetch 100.000 latest entries from API and build model from them. Model does not persist to disc and is currently untested.

Fetch from API

Verify existence of previous model.
If no model is found, calls API to fetch information and merges them together into a a Pandas DataFrame.
